1️⃣ What is Automation?

Automation = using Python to do repetitive tasks automatically

Instead of doing manually, Python does it for you.

🔥 Real-Life Examples

Rename 100 files in seconds

Send automatic emails

Organize folders

Download data automatically

WhatsApp/email bots

2️⃣ File Automation Example

👉 Rename all files in a folder

import os

folder_path = "your_folder_path"

files = os.listdir(folder_path)

for i, file in enumerate(files):
    old_name = os.path.join(folder_path, file)
    new_name = os.path.join(folder_path, f"file_{i}.txt")
    
    os.rename(old_name, new_name)
3️⃣ Automating File Organization
import os
import shutil

source = "your_folder"

for file in os.listdir(source):
    if file.endswith(".jpg"):
        shutil.move(file, "images/")
